title: Beyond the Horror: Cult Episode 11
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Loved this season absolutely. It's now on par with my favorite Asylum. Haven't been this impressed with the writing for a while. I like the supernatural in past seasons but it gets kind of old/predictable.
This season was one of my favorites - possibly my favorite at all.
I agree with Jonas. A theatre theme would be great. Or a sci-fi space with some kind of monster.
So sad this is the finale! I'll miss all of you until next season being all together! BTW where have Casey and Maisy been and will Jonas be back next season??? And good luck with your petition!!! 😊😊😊
Tammy thank you for mentioning The Following. This is an amzing series I have been bindge watching since you mentioned it on Wednesday .
description:
VIDEO CONTAINS SPOILERS FOR American Horror Story, Season 7, Episode 11!!!

Beyond the Horror: Cult, is an unofficial American Horror Story Live After Show. Hosted by MaryGirl Moody.  I discuss and review each episode of American Horror Story Cult.
